title: [Stars of the Sea]
description: A thick padded bench rests before a looming aquarium, offering an ideal vantage to observe its watery world.  Sunlight illuminates a magnificent statue that gazes out a nearby porthole.

A thick padded bench rests before a looming aquarium, offering an ideal vantage to observe its watery world shadowed by night.  Clutched within the unliving hands of a statue, a single candle illuminates this otherwise darkened hold.
